## Partner Management

### Create Partner Config
`POST /fee-share/partner-config/creation-tx`

One partner key per wallet only.

### Get Partner Stats
`GET /fee-share/partner-config/stats`

### Claim Partner Fees
`POST /fee-share/partner-config/claim-tx`

---

## Rate Limits

- 1,000 requests/hour per user
- Applies across all API keys
- Check headers: `X-RateLimit-Remaining`, `X-RateLimit-Reset`

## Error Codes

| Code | Meaning | Retry? |
|------|---------|--------|
| 400 | Bad request | No |
| 401 | Invalid API key | No |
| 403 | No permission | No |
| 404 | Not found | No |
| 413 | File too large | No |
| 429 | Rate limited | Yes, after resetTime |
| 5xx | Server error | Yes, with backoff |
